  "notes": "Champions:\nTough battle abilities. Instant win, limit defender, kill champions.\n\nRealms:\nNo limit attacker or cause attacker to discard so that Logistics rule doesn't work against me.\n\nCombos:\n-Spider attack razed realm and win to bring Drawsemaj into play:\n\nConsidering...:\n-Myalasia, Sir Edmund Bloodsworth\n-slap, deflection\n-curse of the wolves blood, blood of azhul\n-tasselhoff, son of tass, stryck...\n-add one more realm? greater chance of spoils being a realm\n-Fighting Dirty? (so hard to get a chance to play it...)\n-Corruption blood ability and more Awnshegh like The Magian & The Gorgon.\n-Iuz so he can lose, discard realm and bring Drawsemaj into play, Winged boots combo.\n\nRules:\n-The Spider gets spoils when attacking razed realm:\nhttp://oracle.wizards.com/scripts/wa.exe?A2=ind0202C&L=SPELLFIRE-L&P=R2751&I=-3\nHe's awesome, just as good as Tithian if not better...\n-Must discard a realm from play (not from hand) for Drawsemaj to come into play.",
